Two people were killed and two injured in a road accident in Embu County on Monday night.
A boda-boda collided head-on with a private car at Kubukubu, witnesses said. The car was heading to Embu town from Kiritiri market.
The motorcycle rider, who was heading towards Muthatari from Embu town, was overtaking another vehicle when the accident occurred.



